title: Bobby Reveals Future Living Situation + 'Seinfeld's' Jason Alexander Remembers Comedian Jerry Stiller + Bobby’s Brain Test
itunes:title: Bobby Reveals Future Living Situation + 'Seinfeld's' Jason Alexander Remembers Comedian Jerry Stiller + Bobby’s Brain Test
description:
Bobby and his girlfriend Caitlin come on to talk about their living situation after quarantine. Will she be staying in LA? Will she move to Nashville and get her own place? Will she be moving in with Bobby? Jason Alexander (who played George Costanza on 'Seinfeld') comes on to talk about the passing of Jerry Stiller, the slow start of Seinfeld and how he thinks the finale was perceived and Pretty Woman. Plus, Bobby gives us an update on his visit to the brain doctor by giving Amy the tests they gave him!
